 2. Tab State Serialization — How Do You Pass a Tab Between Windows?

To move a tab torn from Window A into Window B, you need to extract the tab's state into a serializable form.

public record TabStateDto(
 string Id,
 string Header,
 string Path,
 int ViewMode,
 int IconSize
);

